history.content:
“Software Engineering in the Industry Q&A” Panel 

Presented by Web Development at Berkeley & The Full Stack Development Decal.

Need help landing a job/internship? Wondering how the experience will be on the job itself? Curious about life after college? Come through to hear from alums - working at Facebook, Apple, Uber, and Okta - on what it's like to work as a full-time engineer!

 When: April 26, Tuesday 6:30-8:00PM

Where: Physics 1 Room

 Speakers:

  • Joey Besgen: Software Engineer At Facebook
  • Manooshree Patel: Sensing HID Watch & Health EPM at Apple
  • Michael Tamaki: Senior Software Engineer at Okta
  • Nik Yerasi: Courier Trip Experience Team SWE at Uber
history.subject: “Software Engineering in the Industry Q&A” Panel hosted by Full Stack Development Decal
